data.text:
Rosângela “Rosinha Garotinho” Barros Assed Matheus de Oliveira, better known simply as Rosinha Garotinho is a Brazilian politician.

Rosângela Matheus was born on April 6, 1963, in Itaperuna, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil. Her birth geographical coordinates are 21° 12’ 18” South latitude and 41° 53’ 16” West longitude. Rosângela Matheus is currently 61 years old.

Astrologically, Rosângela Matheus falls under the Sun sign of Aries, with Cancer as her Ascendant, Virgo as her Moon sign, and Libra as her Black Moon Lilith sign.
